data.description: PRICE IMPROVEMENT-WATERFORD ESTATES- This charismatic home is nestled at the end of a cul-de-sac, providing extra privacy & over size back yard for your enjoyment. Home has been meticulously maintained by the owner, New A/C  Jan 2023, New Roof Dec.  2022, Hot water heater 2021, updated appliances & carpeting. Split bedroom, open floor plan offering plenty of room for entertaining. Kitchen with large island & huge pantry. High ceilings in Great room & dining area overlooking that beautiful back yard. Master bedroom with walk-in closet & another large closet. Dual sinks in Master bath & walk-in shower.  Waterford Estates is a gated community with two pools to choose from plus a gym, bocci ball & pickle ball courts. Located only minuets from Historic Down Town Punta Gorda.
